The base DC for revivification is 10.
  The base increases by 1 every time a character has died and come back to life in the past.
  Assist Checks
    Critical Successes decrease the DC by 4.
    Successful checks decrease the DC by 2.
    Failed checks increase the DC by 1.
    Critical Fails increase the DC by 2.
  After the Dead PC decides to roll to attempt to come back to life, you may choose to tell the PC the DC.
